name: Falling
description: Jennelle decides to go to rehab. Chelsea, in an attempt to get her life together, puts an extra effort into obtaining her GED. She goes to an interview and passes a test. Leah finds out that Corey has hired a lawyer and proactively files for divorce  to ensure she gets custody. Jo starts dropping by to see Isaac during the week and although Kailyn is still dating Jordan, she ends up sleeping with Jo.
